          "notes": "Welcome the audience. Beekeeping, also known as apiculture, is both an ancient practice and a modern hobby that benefits gardens, agriculture, and the environment."
        },
        {
          "type": "content",
          "title": "Why Keep Bees?",
          "content": {
            "bullets": [
              "Pollination support for gardens",
              "Fresh honey production",
              "Beeswax for crafts",
              "Environmental conservation",
              "Fascinating hobby",
              "Connection to nature"
            ]
          },
          "notes": "Beekeeping offers multiple benefits. Pollination increases garden yields by 30-50%. A single hive can produce 25-60 pounds of honey annually."
        }
      ]
    },
